title: Vikings-Seahawks MNF Preview, Worst Week 13 Losses (Football 12/2)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Vikings vs Seahawks on Monday Night Football (5:00). The guys discuss Primetime Russell Wilson vs Primetime Kirk Cousins, the impact of Adam Thielen's injury, how to contain Dalvin Cook, Tyler Lockett's brilliance and Seattle's backfield before they decide on player props and pick the game. Then, Jason La Canfora joins the podcast to break down the AFC Playoff Picture and discuss the worst losses from Week 13.
